{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/applicationcommandlineprotocol\/set(exitstatus:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"exitStatus"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The return value of the [Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/oncommandline(flags:handler:) signal is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passed to this function when the handler returns.  This is the usual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"way of setting the exit status.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In the event that you want the remote invocation to continue running","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and want to decide on the exit status in the future, you can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call.  For the case of a remote invocation, the remote process will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"typically exit when the last reference is dropped on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cmdline"},{"text":".  The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"exit status of the remote process will be equal to the last value"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that was set with this function."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the case that the commandline invocation is local, the situation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is slightly more complicated.  If the commandline invocation results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in the mainloop running (ie: because the use-count of the application","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"increased to a non-zero value) then the application is considered to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have been ‘successful’ in a certain sense, and the exit status is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"always zero.  If the application use count is zero, though, the exit","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status of the local "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLine","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is used.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is a no-op if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_application_command_line_done()"},{"text":" has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"been called."}]}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the exit status that will be used when the invoking process"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"exits.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO30ApplicationCommandLineProtocolPAAE3set10exitStatusySi_tF","title":"set(exitStatus:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"exitStatus","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol\/set(exitStatus:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol/set(exitStatus:)":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol\/set(exitStatus:)","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the exit status that will be used when the invoking process"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"exits."}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationcommandlineprotocol\/set(exitstatus:)","title":"set(exitStatus:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"exitStatus","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationCommandLine":{"title":"ApplicationCommandLine","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ApplicationCommandLine","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApplicationCommandLine"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationcommandline","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLine","abstract":[{"code":"GApplicationCommandLine","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" represents a command-line invocation of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"an application.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApplicationCommandLineProtocol"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationcommandlineprotocol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GApplicationCommandLine"},{"text":" represents a command-line invocation of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"an application.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationCommandLineProtocol","title":"ApplicationCommandLineProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApplicationCommandLineProtocol"}]}}}